description:
Luffy and his crew make their way towards Arlong Park and a showdown with its fishy proprietor. Along the way, they discover a treasure map that raises more questions about Nami.
Source: crunchyroll

titles.title: La disparition d`Usopp ? A quand le débarquement de Luffy ?
